title: RHOP: Simply the Breasts
description:
The trip to Williamsburg continues to be bumpy for The Real Housewives of Potomac as Gizelle and Robyn questions Wendy's "substance" in light of recent physical enhancements. Plus, Karen reminds us of her commitment to lift women up, not tear them down...

This episode is a Crappens on Demand recap. Be sure to watch it here: https://www.patreon.com/posts/54989453

Our Patreon Extras: https://patreon.com/watchwhatcrappens
